Summary Stats

d %>%
  select(overallScore, avgScore, palateScore, aromaScore, tasteScore, appearanceScore, reviewLength, userID) %>%
  gather(scoreType, score, -userID) %>%
  group_by(scoreType) %>%
  summarise(mu = mean(score),
            sd = sd(score))
